  <description type="morphology">Distal laminal cells weakly convex superficially, adaxial surface of costa not mammillose.  Seta elongate.  Capsule cylindrical, stegocarpous but never cleisto-carpous.  Spores granulose, low-papillose or spiculose, large, 28–39 µm.</description>
